title: SEA SLUG DIVERS Malapascua

review.description: Did several dives with them and I think the team was very professional and friendly! With rates that are very competitive and a great staff I highly recommend them for your next diving adventure...
Best diving rates on the island. Fun dives at only PHP 1,200 per dive. Friendly staff and divemasters!
